node.text: category is WOMEN and no one can tell me otherwise! my community always has my back. it’s so easy to feel alone but there’s a whole world waiting to love u. we will continue to celebrate and fight for our equality no matter what. this month and every month. always walk with pride. #happypride 🌈

node.text: @dragunbeauty x @instagram SOLD OUT 🌈 i started my beauty brand 2 years ago becoming one of the first Trans CEOs. no one believed in my products catering to Trans people and all people... 2 years later we have built a global beauty empire that continues to break records and stigmas for the LGBTQIA+. thank u Instagram for partnering with my brand for #pridemonth to make my products accessible to everyone! thank u to my entire Dragun Beauty team for ur hard work in pulling this off. but mostly thank u to u guys for supporting my little orange correctors and dragun eggs. u have always believed in me even when i didn’t. thank u happy pride! ❤️🧡💛💚💙💜
